# Applying API Governance Part 1 :: How can consumers find the right APIs?

Ensuring that APIs can easily be identified and found is overlooked by the API Developers. This article puts some recommendations in place to ensure consumers can find your APIs quickly and efficiently.

I have just published this article on my personal blog. Please take a look at
https://chrisphillips-cminion.github.io/apiconnect/2020/07/31/apigov1.html
